Third-party notices
===================

This project is a Swift port of mlx-MoGe (https://github.com/mnmly/mlx-MoGe),
a Python MLX port of MoGe (https://github.com/microsoft/MoGe). Both upstream
projects are MIT licensed:

    MIT License
    Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation.

    MIT License
    Copyright (c) 2026 mnmly

